{"tid":1374006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正確示範]同我推上去，正確應對冒警暴徒","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T18:16:16.000Z","uid":45788,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec869950d76a77dfc4a1044b2fbf759cbed7028","tid":1374006,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3056456287760678&amp;id=100001890094556&amp;sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3056456287760678%26id%3D100001890094556%26sfnsn%3Dmo&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F156X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=2e67618b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3056456287760678&amp;id=100001890094556&amp;sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你冇委任證點證明你係警察先<br />\n搞唔好你就係白衫暴徒wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不要說:好好好冷靜我攞<br />\n<br />\n要說:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">委任證呢，我懷疑你冒警喎</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/fact-check-%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%93%BE%E4%BA%82%E8%A6%96%E8%81%BD-%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89%E5%95%A6%E6%9F%92%E6%92%9A%E6%87%B5%E6%87%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ffact-check-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%2593%25BE%25E4%25BA%2582%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%2581%25BD-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2595%25A6%25E6%259F%2592%25E6%2592%259A%25E6%2587%25B5%25E6%2587%25B5%2F&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F156X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=b381cd99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ffact-check-%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%2593%25BE%25E4%25BA%2582%25E8%25A6%2596%25E8%2581%25BD-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A7%2594%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2595%25A6%25E6%259F%2592%25E6%2592%259A%25E6%2587%25B5%25E6%2587%25B5%2F&h=64341d7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/fact-check-%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E6%93%BE%E4%BA%82%E8%A6%96%E8%81%BD-%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89%E5%95%A6%E6%9F%92%E6%92%9A%E6%87%B5%E6%87%B5/</a><br />\n<br />\n《警察通例》第 20-14 條第 4 段如是說：<br />\n「如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員應出示委任證，除非：<br />\n(a) 情況不容許；或<br />\n(b) 出示委任證會影響警隊行動及／或危及有關人員的安全；或<br />\n(c) 要求不合理。」<br />\n<br />\n警訊都有教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2019/06/警察委任證-警訊-20190628225508_23b4_small.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2019%2F06%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89-%E8%AD%A6%E8%A8%8A-20190628225508_23b4_small.png&h=d32ce298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無證，我地有合理懷疑佢地冒警<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇證啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攞翻個委任證咪比你睇到飽囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0f506af4824cf75bb9bcd77854cb4c4b8ec6fa","tid":1374006,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,